{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/blog/top-3-cycling-shoes/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Top 3 Shoes","content":"\n<p>A number of you have asked us whether there were cycling shoes that worked particularly well with the Stryde bike. First off &#8211; any reliable cycling shoes that are compatible with SPD clips or even sneakers will work! But of course we have a few favorites, and we wanted to share them with you.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. TIEM shoes. This Boston-based company (go Beantown fitness scene!) launched just a few years ago, but has since then accumulated a legion of fans in indoor cycling world, us included. The concept of a SPD shoe that doubles up as a sneaker that you can wear off the bike has been around for a while, but TIEM executed it to perfection. Beautiful design, extremely high level of comfort, and high quality &#8211; trifecta that makes this brand our favorite. There are plentiful color options too. The only drawback? No men&#8217;s line! We sure hope it comes out soon.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-attachment-id=\"85\" data-permalink=\"https://strydebike1.wordpress.com/61tmrvxcerl-_ac_ux500_/\" data-orig-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"500,269\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_.jpg?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_.jpg?w=500\" src=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_.jpg?w=500\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-85\" srcset=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_.jpg 500w, https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_.jpg?w=150 150w, https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/61tmrvxcerl._ac_ux500_.jpg?w=300 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><figcaption>TIEM Cycling Shoes</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Tommaso Pista shoes. Ok, first off this company definitely sounds like an Italian firm with 100+ year old heritage. We give kudos to awesome branding for this Denver, Colorado bike manufacturer that has expanded into cycling shoes for bikers, and make a shoe that&#8217;s equally loved by indoor cyclists! Beautiful, modern, solid, and sturdy, this shoe have highly comfortable padding and are clearly built to last. The heel support is excellent &#8211; just make sure your order the right size, they run a bit small.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-attachment-id=\"86\" data-permalink=\"https://strydebike1.wordpress.com/71r2u1fhprl-_ac_ux395_/\" data-orig-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"395,393\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_.jpg?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_.jpg?w=395\" src=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_.jpg?w=395\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-86\" srcset=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_.jpg 395w, https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_.jpg?w=150 150w, https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/71r2u1fhprl._ac_ux395_.jpg?w=300 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 395px) 100vw, 395px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>3. Shimano Men&#8217;s CT500&nbsp;Shoe</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For male riders who are craving something similar to TIEM shoes, these Shimano ones are a solid choice. The price is compelling too, but there are a few riders who complained about the fit. Make sure you buy at a place with a good return policy! But most likely you will love them.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img data-attachment-id=\"87\" data-permalink=\"https://strydebike1.wordpress.com/41b6l2czll/\" data-orig-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/41b6l2czll.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"500,274\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"41b6l2czll\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/41b6l2czll.jpg?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/41b6l2czll.jpg?w=500\" src=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/41b6l2czll.jpg?w=500\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-87\" srcset=\"https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/41b6l2czll.jpg 500w, https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/41b6l2czll.jpg?w=150 150w, https://strydebike1.files.wordpress.com/2020/03/41b6l2czll.jpg?w=300 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></figure>\n"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Katana Fitnes Site"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"ac2a0c0b-1dbd-5b4c-89e0-0656bf5ebc50"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}